# Keep the build context small and never ship secrets.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/dist
**/build

# Secrets / env
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Python pipeline (not part of the web image)
pipeline/
**/__pycache__
**/.venv

# VCS / CI / docs / local
.git
.github
docs/
*.md
**/*.md
db/
docker-compose.yml
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/*.tsbuildinfo
